Responders's actions after 1NT forcing:

A. New suit on 2-level : Non-forcing
B. Preference to opener's Major : Typically weak, usually 2-card support
C. Raise of opener's second suit: Invitational, natural
D. 2NT : Invitational, Natural
E. Jump Raise of opener's major: 3-card limit raise|
